| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3945 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 24ecbb48-f1f6-5f43-ae80-16ae386feeb8"
